          "reviewBody": "Spent 5 years of my life from ukg to class 5th in this school (2010-2015) and man I gotta say they were the best years of my life. The teachers , the friends and everything else was perfect. Still remember standing outside the line for not polishing my shoes and students of those years might remember the guy Tarun Sagar ( I am not him ). How I wish I could have spent atleast 5 more years in that school but who can change the inevitable. I cherish those memories and I have to say that even tho I might not be as academically good as I was at that time , the core principles and discipline is still ingrained in me and it's all thanks to this school.",
